  "text": "For Tian Tian's samples, analysis was performed through measurement of ferri-oxidase activity using N,N-dimethyl-p-phenylenediamine oxidase as a substrate (DPP; Sigma-Aldrich, UK) as optimised by Sunderman and Nomoto [CITATION_1] and modified for a Cobas Fara centrifugal analyser. Undiluted urine was analysed, and the presence of ceruloplasmin was indicated by a quantifiable pink/purple colour.",
